            . I am a Police-constable. I took the prisoner on the 16th of April, in the Hackney-road; Mrs. Conner and 
               <persName id="t18310630-38-person396">
                  Robert 
                  Hughes
               <interp inst="t18310630-38-person396" type="surname" value="Hughes"></interp>
